---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="About - Beau Crisp">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8">About Beau Crisp</h1>

    <div class="prose lg:prose-xl">
      <p class="mb-6">
        With over a decade of experience in strength and conditioning, I've
        helped hundreds of clients achieve their fitness goals through
        personalized coaching and evidence-based training methods.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">Qualifications</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-6">
        <li>Certified Strength and Conditioning Specialist (CSCS)</li>
        <li>Master's Degree in Exercise Science</li>
        <li>Performance Enhancement Specialist</li>
        <li>Former Division I Athlete</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">My Approach</h2>
      <p class="mb-6">
        I believe in a holistic approach to fitness that combines strength
        training, conditioning, and proper recovery. Every client receives a
        customized program that takes into account their goals, experience
        level, and lifestyle.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">Why Choose Me</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-6">
        <li>Personalized attention and program design</li>
        <li>Regular progress tracking and program adjustments</li>
        <li>Evidence-based training methods</li>
        <li>Supportive and motivating environment</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
